{"tid":1903397,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"最近美國又捉到兩個支那技術間諜","createTime":"2020-02-29T02:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T06:06:41.000Z","uid":48083,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c59467710e7cd022b15a2b8c78d18e9c457a9c82","tid":1903397,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:46:59.000Z","msg":"美國逮捕了一名隱瞞與中國大學聯繫的華裔教授。<br />\n<br />\n司法部星期四(2月27日)宣佈，田納西大學諾克斯維爾分校(UTK)機械航空與生物醫學工程系副教授胡安明(Anming Hu)在當天被捕。他受到聯邦起訴，被控犯有三項電信欺詐罪和三項做出虛假陳述罪。<br />\n<br />\n司法部負責國家安全的助理部長約翰&middot;C&middot;德默斯(John C. Demers)說：「胡據稱在從美國宇航局(NASA)獲取經費的同時掩藏他與一所中國大學的關係從而犯有欺詐罪。這只是涉及教授和研究人員向他們的美國雇主及美國政府隱瞞他們與中國關係的最新案例。對此我們不會容忍。」<br />\n<br />\n田納西東區聯邦檢察官J&middot;道格拉斯&middot;歐佛貝(J. Douglas Overbey)說：「對旨在破壞聯邦法律所規定的與中國及中國大學有關的資金限制的欺詐行為，美國檢察官辦公室予以嚴肅對待。」<br />\n<br />\n起訴書指稱，從2016年開始，胡安明展開了一場騙局，向NASA隱瞞他與北京工業大學(BJUT)的聯繫。聯邦法律禁止NASA把撥款用於與中國或中國大學合作的項目。起訴書稱，由於胡安明所作的謊報和漏報，田納西大學諾克斯維爾分校錯誤地向美國宇航局認證該校符合該項聯邦法律。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/a-professor-at-utk-arrested-for-hiding-ties-with-a-chinese-university-20200227/5307950.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fa-professor-at-utk-arrested-for-hiding-ties-with-a-chinese-university-20200227%2F5307950.html&d=OftESTy%2BPOS3A4jdltYT24DCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=34953f30\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/a-professor-at-utk-arrested-for-hiding-ties-with-a-chinese-university-20200227/5307950.html</a><br />\n<br />\n哩條友係攻半導體技術￼￼<br />\nAnd while Hu is not accused of anything espionage-related, former US intelligence officer Nicholas Eftimiades, an expert on Chinese espionage operations, said Hu&rsquo;s general field of study&mdash;nanomanufacturing and laser-based processing&mdash;would be of great interest to China.<br />\n<br />\n「This technology has very specific applications in etching semiconductors that are critical to the Chinese government,」 Eftimiades told Quartz. 「It is an area in which they lag behind us and have been trying to become self-reliant. Well, self-reliant in production, not in developing the technology themselves. That, they steal.」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qz.com/1809851/tennessee-professor-charged-with-hiding-china-ties-from-nasa/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqz.com%2F1809851%2Ftennessee-professor-charged-with-hiding-china-ties-from-nasa%2F&d=OftESTy%2BPOS3A4jdltYT24DCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=38d61b53\" target=\"_blank\">https://qz.com/1809851/tennessee-professor-charged-with-hiding-china-ties-from-nasa/</a><br />\n<br />\n另一個認咗偷下一代電池技術￼￼￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nChinese scientist Hongjin Tan gets two-year prison sentence for stealing trade secrets from US energy company<br />\n<br />\nHongjin Tan, who worked on the research and development of next-generation battery technologies for Phillips 66, had pleaded guilty<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3052784/chinese-scientist-hongjin-tan-gets-two-year-prison-sentence\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fdiplomacy%2Farticle%2F3052784%2Fchinese-scientist-hongjin-tan-gets-two-year-prison-sentence&d=OftESTy%2BPOS3A4jdltYT24DCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=abfbd7fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3052784/chinese-scientist-hongjin-tan-gets-two-year-prison-sentence</a>"},{"pid":"c3b21a74bcae67e08564533cecc5d0294857c006","tid":1903397,"uid":299694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T03:54:16.000Z","msg":"仆街支狗"},{"pid":"1b52dff06140f4b1c76a3bf62dc2d1f5f34b0b5f","tid":1903397,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T05:47:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pi